21#include <isc/regex.h>

23/*
24 * Check the wire format of the Regexp field.
25 * Don't allow embeded NUL's.
26 */
27static inline isc_result_t
28txt_valid_regex(const unsigned char *txt) {
29 unsigned int nsub = 0;
30 char regex[256];
31 char *cp;
32 bool flags = false;
33 bool replace = false;
34 unsigned char c;
35 unsigned char delim;
36 unsigned int len;
37 int n;
38
39 len = *txt++;
40 if (len == 0U)
41 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
42
43 delim = *txt++;
44 len--;
45
46 /*
47 * Digits, backslash and flags can't be delimiters.
48 */
49 switch (delim) {
50 case '0': case '1': case '2': case '3': case '4':
51 case '5': case '6': case '7': case '8': case '9':
52 case '\\': case 'i': case 0:
53 return (DNS_R_SYNTAX);
54 }
55
56 cp = regex;
57 while (len-- > 0) {
58 c = *txt++;
59 if (c == 0)
60 return (DNS_R_SYNTAX);
61 if (c == delim && !replace) {
62 replace = true;
63 continue;
64 } else if (c == delim && !flags) {
65 flags = true;
66 continue;
67 } else if (c == delim)
68 return (DNS_R_SYNTAX);
69 /*
70 * Flags are not escaped.
71 */
72 if (flags) {
73 switch (c) {
74 case 'i':
75 continue;
76 default:
77 return (DNS_R_SYNTAX);
78 }
79 }
80 if (!replace)
81 *cp++ = c;
82 if (c == '\\') {
83 if (len == 0)
84 return (DNS_R_SYNTAX);
85 c = *txt++;
86 if (c == 0)
87 return (DNS_R_SYNTAX);
88 len--;
89 if (replace)
90 switch (c) {
91 case '0': return (DNS_R_SYNTAX);
92 case '1': if (nsub < 1) nsub = 1; break;
93 case '2': if (nsub < 2) nsub = 2; break;
94 case '3': if (nsub < 3) nsub = 3; break;
95 case '4': if (nsub < 4) nsub = 4; break;
96 case '5': if (nsub < 5) nsub = 5; break;
97 case '6': if (nsub < 6) nsub = 6; break;
98 case '7': if (nsub < 7) nsub = 7; break;
99 case '8': if (nsub < 8) nsub = 8; break;
100 case '9': if (nsub < 9) nsub = 9; break;
101 }
102 if (!replace)
103 *cp++ = c;
104 }
105 }
106 if (!flags)
107 return (DNS_R_SYNTAX);
108 *cp = '\0';
109 n = isc_regex_validate(regex);
110 if (n < 0 || nsub > (unsigned int)n)
111 return (DNS_R_SYNTAX);
112 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
113}

115static inline isc_result_t
116fromtext_naptr(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
117 isc_token_t token;
118 dns_name_t name;
119 isc_buffer_t buffer;
120 unsigned char *regex;
121
122 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_naptr);
123
124 UNUSED(type);
125 UNUSED(rdclass);
126 UNUSED(callbacks);
127
128 /*
129 * Order.
130 */
131 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
132 false));
133 if (token.value.as_ulong > 0xffffU)
134 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
135 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong, target));
136
137 /*
138 * Preference.
139 */
140 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
141 false));
142 if (token.value.as_ulong > 0xffffU)
143 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
144 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong, target));
145
146 /*
147 * Flags.
148 */
149 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_qstring,
150 false));
151 RETTOK(txt_fromtext(&token.value.as_textregion, target));
152
153 /*
154 * Service.
155 */
156 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_qstring,
157 false));
158 RETTOK(txt_fromtext(&token.value.as_textregion, target));
159
160 /*
161 * Regexp.
162 */
163 regex = isc_buffer_used(target);
164 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_qstring,
165 false));
166 RETTOK(txt_fromtext(&token.value.as_textregion, target));
167 RETTOK(txt_valid_regex(regex));
168
169 /*
170 * Replacement.
171 */
172 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
173 false));
174 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
175 buffer_fromregion(&buffer, &token.value.as_region);
176 if (origin == NULL)
177 origin = dns_rootname;
178 RETTOK(dns_name_fromtext(&name, &buffer, origin, options, target));
179 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
180}

182static inline isc_result_t
183totext_naptr(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
184 isc_region_t region;
185 dns_name_t name;
186 dns_name_t prefix;
187 bool sub;
188 char buf[sizeof("64000")];
189 unsigned short num;
190
191 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_naptr);
192 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
193
194 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
195 dns_name_init(&prefix, NULL);
196
197 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
198
199 /*
200 * Order.
201 */
202 num = uint16_fromregion(&region);
203 isc_region_consume(&region, 2);
204 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%u", num);
205 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
206 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
207
208 /*
209 * Preference.
210 */
211 num = uint16_fromregion(&region);
212 isc_region_consume(&region, 2);
213 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%u", num);
214 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
215 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
216
217 /*
218 * Flags.
219 */
220 RETERR(txt_totext(&region, true, target));
221 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
222
223 /*
224 * Service.
225 */
226 RETERR(txt_totext(&region, true, target));
227 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
228
229 /*
230 * Regexp.
231 */
232 RETERR(txt_totext(&region, true, target));
233 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
234
235 /*
236 * Replacement.
237 */
238 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
239 sub = name_prefix(&name, tctx->origin, &prefix);
240 return (dns_name_totext(&prefix, sub, target));
241}

243static inline isc_result_t
244fromwire_naptr(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
245 dns_name_t name;
246 isc_region_t sr;
247 unsigned char *regex;
248
249 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_naptr);
250
251 UNUSED(type);
252 UNUSED(rdclass);
253
254 dns_decompress_setmethods(dctx, DNS_COMPRESS_NONE);
255
256 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
257
258 /*
259 * Order, preference.
260 */
261 isc_buffer_activeregion(source, &sr);
262 if (sr.length < 4)
263 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
264 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, 4));
265 isc_buffer_forward(source, 4);
266
267 /*
268 * Flags.
269 */
270 RETERR(txt_fromwire(source, target));
271
272 /*
273 * Service.
274 */
275 RETERR(txt_fromwire(source, target));
276
277 /*
278 * Regexp.
279 */
280 regex = isc_buffer_used(target);
281 RETERR(txt_fromwire(source, target));
282 RETERR(txt_valid_regex(regex));
283
284 /*
285 * Replacement.
286 */
287 return (dns_name_fromwire(&name, source, dctx, options, target));
288}

290static inline isc_result_t
291towire_naptr(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
292 dns_name_t name;
293 dns_offsets_t offsets;
294 isc_region_t sr;
295
296 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_naptr);
297 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
298
299 dns_compress_setmethods(cctx, DNS_COMPRESS_NONE);
300 /*
301 * Order, preference.
302 */
303 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
304 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, 4));
305 isc_region_consume(&sr, 4);
306
307 /*
308 * Flags.
309 */
310 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, sr.base[0] + 1));
311 isc_region_consume(&sr, sr.base[0] + 1);
312
313 /*
314 * Service.
315 */
316 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, sr.base[0] + 1));
317 isc_region_consume(&sr, sr.base[0] + 1);
318
319 /*
320 * Regexp.
321 */
322 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, sr.base[0] + 1));
323 isc_region_consume(&sr, sr.base[0] + 1);
324
325 /*
326 * Replacement.
327 */
328 dns_name_init(&name, offsets);
329 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &sr);
330 return (dns_name_towire(&name, cctx, target));
331}

333static inline int
334compare_naptr(ARGS_COMPARE) {
335 dns_name_t name1;
336 dns_name_t name2;
337 isc_region_t region1;
338 isc_region_t region2;
339 int order, len;
340
341 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
342 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
343 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_naptr);
344 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
345 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
346
347 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &region1);
348 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &region2);
349
350 /*
351 * Order, preference.
352 */
353 order = memcmp(region1.base, region2.base, 4);
354 if (order != 0)
355 return (order < 0 ? -1 : 1);
356 isc_region_consume(&region1, 4);
357 isc_region_consume(&region2, 4);
358
359 /*
360 * Flags.
361 */
362 len = ISC_MIN(region1.base[0], region2.base[0]);
363 order = memcmp(region1.base, region2.base, len + 1);
364 if (order != 0)
365 return (order < 0 ? -1 : 1);
366 isc_region_consume(&region1, region1.base[0] + 1);
367 isc_region_consume(&region2, region2.base[0] + 1);
368
369 /*
370 * Service.
371 */
372 len = ISC_MIN(region1.base[0], region2.base[0]);
373 order = memcmp(region1.base, region2.base, len + 1);
374 if (order != 0)
375 return (order < 0 ? -1 : 1);
376 isc_region_consume(&region1, region1.base[0] + 1);
377 isc_region_consume(&region2, region2.base[0] + 1);
378
379 /*
380 * Regexp.
381 */
382 len = ISC_MIN(region1.base[0], region2.base[0]);
383 order = memcmp(region1.base, region2.base, len + 1);
384 if (order != 0)
385 return (order < 0 ? -1 : 1);
386 isc_region_consume(&region1, region1.base[0] + 1);
387 isc_region_consume(&region2, region2.base[0] + 1);
388
389 /*
390 * Replacement.
391 */
392 dns_name_init(&name1, NULL);
393 dns_name_init(&name2, NULL);
394
395 dns_name_fromregion(&name1, &region1);
396 dns_name_fromregion(&name2, &region2);
397
398 return (dns_name_rdatacompare(&name1, &name2));
399}

401static inline isc_result_t
402fromstruct_naptr(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
403 dns_rdata_naptr_t *naptr = source;
404 isc_region_t region;
405
406 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_naptr);
407 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
408 REQUIRE(naptr->common.rdtype == type);
409 REQUIRE(naptr->common.rdclass == rdclass);
410 REQUIRE(naptr->flags != NULL || naptr->flags_len == 0);
411 REQUIRE(naptr->service != NULL || naptr->service_len == 0);
412 REQUIRE(naptr->regexp != NULL || naptr->regexp_len == 0);
413
414 UNUSED(type);
415 UNUSED(rdclass);
416
417 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(naptr->order, target));
418 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(naptr->preference, target));
419 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(naptr->flags_len, target));
420 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, naptr->flags, naptr->flags_len));
421 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(naptr->service_len, target));
422 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, naptr->service, naptr->service_len));
423 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(naptr->regexp_len, target));
424 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, naptr->regexp, naptr->regexp_len));
425 dns_name_toregion(&naptr->replacement, &region);
426 return (isc_buffer_copyregion(target, &region));
427}
428
429static inline isc_result_t
430tostruct_naptr(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
431 dns_rdata_naptr_t *naptr = target;
432 isc_region_t r;
433 isc_result_t result;
434 dns_name_t name;
435
436 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_naptr);
437 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
438 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
439
440 naptr->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
441 naptr->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
442 ISC_LINK_INIT(&naptr->common, link);
443
444 naptr->flags = NULL;
445 naptr->service = NULL;
446 naptr->regexp = NULL;
447
448 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
449
450 naptr->order = uint16_fromregion(&r);
451 isc_region_consume(&r, 2);
452
453 naptr->preference = uint16_fromregion(&r);
454 isc_region_consume(&r, 2);
455
456 naptr->flags_len = uint8_fromregion(&r);
457 isc_region_consume(&r, 1);
458 INSIST(naptr->flags_len <= r.length);
459 naptr->flags = mem_maybedup(mctx, r.base, naptr->flags_len);
460 if (naptr->flags == NULL)
461 goto cleanup;
462 isc_region_consume(&r, naptr->flags_len);
463
464 naptr->service_len = uint8_fromregion(&r);
465 isc_region_consume(&r, 1);
466 INSIST(naptr->service_len <= r.length);
467 naptr->service = mem_maybedup(mctx, r.base, naptr->service_len);
468 if (naptr->service == NULL)
469 goto cleanup;
470 isc_region_consume(&r, naptr->service_len);
471
472 naptr->regexp_len = uint8_fromregion(&r);
473 isc_region_consume(&r, 1);
474 INSIST(naptr->regexp_len <= r.length);
475 naptr->regexp = mem_maybedup(mctx, r.base, naptr->regexp_len);
476 if (naptr->regexp == NULL)
477 goto cleanup;
478 isc_region_consume(&r, naptr->regexp_len);
479
480 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
481 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &r);
482 dns_name_init(&naptr->replacement, NULL);
483 result = name_duporclone(&name, mctx, &naptr->replacement);
484 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
485 goto cleanup;
486 naptr->mctx = mctx;
487 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
488
489 cleanup:
490 if (mctx != NULL && naptr->flags != NULL)
491 isc_mem_free(mctx, naptr->flags);
492 if (mctx != NULL && naptr->service != NULL)
493 isc_mem_free(mctx, naptr->service);
494 if (mctx != NULL && naptr->regexp != NULL)
495 isc_mem_free(mctx, naptr->regexp);
496 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
497}
498
499static inline void
500freestruct_naptr(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
501 dns_rdata_naptr_t *naptr = source;
502
503 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
504 REQUIRE(naptr->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_naptr);
505
506 if (naptr->mctx == NULL)
507 return;
508
509 if (naptr->flags != NULL)
510 isc_mem_free(naptr->mctx, naptr->flags);
511 if (naptr->service != NULL)
512 isc_mem_free(naptr->mctx, naptr->service);
513 if (naptr->regexp != NULL)
514 isc_mem_free(naptr->mctx, naptr->regexp);
515 dns_name_free(&naptr->replacement, naptr->mctx);
516 naptr->mctx = NULL;
517}

519static inline isc_result_t
520additionaldata_naptr(ARGS_ADDLDATA) {
521 dns_name_t name;
522 dns_offsets_t offsets;
523 isc_region_t sr;
524 dns_rdatatype_t atype;
525 unsigned int i, flagslen;
526 char *cp;
527
528 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_naptr);
529
530 /*
531 * Order, preference.
532 */
533 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
534 isc_region_consume(&sr, 4);
535
536 /*
537 * Flags.
538 */
539 atype = 0;
540 flagslen = sr.base[0];
541 cp = (char *)&sr.base[1];
542 for (i = 0; i < flagslen; i++, cp++) {
543 if (*cp == 'S' || *cp == 's') {
544 atype = dns_rdatatype_srv;
545 break;
546 }
547 if (*cp == 'A' || *cp == 'a') {
548 atype = dns_rdatatype_a;
549 break;
550 }
551 }
552 isc_region_consume(&sr, flagslen + 1);
553
554 /*
555 * Service.
556 */
557 isc_region_consume(&sr, sr.base[0] + 1);
558
559 /*
560 * Regexp.
561 */
562 isc_region_consume(&sr, sr.base[0] + 1);
563
564 /*
565 * Replacement.
566 */
567 dns_name_init(&name, offsets);
568 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &sr);
569
570 if (atype != 0)
571 return ((add)(arg, &name, atype));
572
573 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
574}

576static inline isc_result_t
577digest_naptr(ARGS_DIGEST) {
578 isc_region_t r1, r2;
579 unsigned int length, n;
580 isc_result_t result;
581 dns_name_t name;
582
583 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_naptr);
584
585 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r1);
586 r2 = r1;
587 length = 0;
588
589 /*
590 * Order, preference.
591 */
592 length += 4;
593 isc_region_consume(&r2, 4);
594
595 /*
596 * Flags.
597 */
598 n = r2.base[0] + 1;
599 length += n;
600 isc_region_consume(&r2, n);
601
602 /*
603 * Service.
604 */
605 n = r2.base[0] + 1;
606 length += n;
607 isc_region_consume(&r2, n);
608
609 /*
610 * Regexp.
611 */
612 n = r2.base[0] + 1;
613 length += n;
614 isc_region_consume(&r2, n);
615
616 /*
617 * Digest the RR up to the replacement name.
618 */
619 r1.length = length;
620 result = (digest)(arg, &r1);
621 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
622 return (result);
623
624 /*
625 * Replacement.
626 */
627
628 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
629 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &r2);
630
631 return (dns_name_digest(&name, digest, arg));
632}
